TERRAFROM - PRIVATE VPN AUTOMATION:

In this demo, i  automate a VPN with private and public 
subnets and place an AMI instance in the public subnet which has an 
internet getway to allow outside traffic.

the terrafrom Project consits of 2 stages (Building a VPN network and creating a httpd 
a web server)

Building the vpn

stage 1: aws-cli permissions
stage 2: Building a VPC
stage 3: attaching an iternet gatewat to the vpc
stage 4: Creating a route table:
stage 5: Creating subet-groups
stage 5: Assotiating the subnets to the route table

Building an AMI-instance

stage 1: creting a web-server and placing it a public subnet
stage 2: attaching a security group that allows (https, http and ssh)
stage 3: attaching a network interface to the web-server
stage 4: installing httpd using userdata 
